image_analysis.description: A photograph of a kitchen interior. The scene shows a stainless steel gas stove with a tan towel hanging on the oven handle, white cabinetry, a white countertop, a small toaster oven, a white wire dish rack, and a stainless steel sink with a faucet. Several bottles of soap (including Mrs. Meyer's brand) are next to the sink. A white door with a brass knob is on the left. A white paper label with the letters 'CC' is taped to the upper left cabinet/door area.

stamps_or_markings: Evidence or exhibit label marked 'CC' taped to the door/cabinet.

notes: The image appears to be a piece of evidence documentation from an investigation, indicated by the 'CC' label and the 'EFTA' tracking number at the bottom right.
